dct_title_s: Map of the central part of Jasper Park, Alberta
dct_description_sm: Canada. Department of the Interior. Topographical Survey "From photographic Surveyss by M. P. Bridgland, D.L.S., 1915 and from Interprovincial Boundary Surveys, 1917 and 1921." Relief shown by 100 feet contours and spot elevation.
